Detailed Description

cvmx_sriomaint::_erb_err_det

The Error Detect Register indicates physical layer transmission errors detected by the hardware. The hardware will not update this register (i.e. this register is locked) while SRIOMAINT()_ERB_ATTR_CAPT[VALID] is set.
